{"tid":1072312,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"左後背好痛","createTime":"2019-03-22T02:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T14:50:53.000Z","uid":50157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf18377b7d8fc7a35a0efb600fd6ed8e8c3fda5","tid":1072312,"uid":50157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:49:01.000Z","msg":"我本身有操開 <br />\n上個禮拜開始左邊上背開始好痛 <br />\n之後拉下個個位既筋 點知仲痛左 <br />\n日日都有搽下d按摩膏 貼埋止痛貼 <br />\n但係過左成個星期都無好過 愈黎愈痛 <br />\n郁下條頸打個乞嗤都好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依一兩日會去睇醫生 但係唔知睇普通西醫定中醫好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無巴打有推介<br />\n<br />\n示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfCF3cA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfCF3cA.png&h=0a6bce6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e71973e3dcf9e4d1d05274504c52b07359475edb","tid":1072312,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"生骨刺"},{"pid":"9cb131f3cbd3b739f8d008d12ad8909d246a4d6d","tid":1072312,"uid":50157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e71973e3dcf9e4d1d05274504c52b07359475edb","tid":1072312,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:00:20.000Z","msg":"生骨刺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:16:55.000Z","msg":"無手腳麻痺喎"},{"pid":"c00353a2e3cb46d5fc09ba1cfeebe0703efec299","tid":1072312,"uid":50157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208fd59d8054d701dd22a86c08c4dfdef1273362","tid":1072312,"uid":163641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:12:19.000Z","msg":"我之前都試過呢個位痛<br />\n睇過西醫無咩作用<br />\n試過拎按摩槍打完直頭訓落床轉身都痛<br />\n後尾去左藥房買消炎止痛食好返<br />\n發緊炎唔好拉唔好按 會傷上加傷<br />\n唔知你係咪同我同一情況 但你可以試下<br />\n消左炎先再拉返鬆佢 唔好之後操野會再傷返發炎（試過）"},{"pid":"17c7f62865e2a6a6728b